{"tid":2051011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（64係鄰國的事？）連登仔肯定係個天跌把鎗落黎都識用的人","createTime":"2020-06-04T12:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T16:01:17.000Z","uid":143608,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0129e5b828b6f71e7dc88f793c6a691ae2a9c819","tid":2051011,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;64係鄰國的事，關香港人咩事&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n呢句算係我聽過最on 9的說話之一<br />\n<br />\n1. 今日的香港依然俾當年64的共產黨政權統治緊，唔通  你自己呃自己，話中共係鄰國的事，同香港人無關？<br />\n<br />\n2. 當年64絕對係香港人民主意識同反共心態的一個轉捩點，香港人參與度之高，黃雀行動呢啲都唔洗多講。有無諗過今時今日咁多中老年手足反共的原因係咩？<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果你講得出64係鄰國的事，咁點解你仲要去玩國際戰線？ 人地都可以話香港係鄰國的事。<br />\n<br />\n要知道，依家基本上全球抗共，64呢個世界上咁標誌的事，基本上唔理你係中國人定香港人，基本上自由世界的人都會關注，64仲係世界各國對中共的一樣武器。今年連美國國務院仲要搞網上64集會。 你仲話64唔關你事？<br />\n<br />\n再退一步，係人都知反送中後，每一個抗爭行動都唔可以放過，更何況64真係connect都好多人。政治潔癖係咪要放低？"},{"pid":"2c48b6c1bd434dcc6346872c4728334cb0a43d2b","tid":2051011,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"標題係唔識用，打少個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320876eed527e2b8427a1371a201cb9ed60b5389","tid":2051011,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6be2ac4a5a56b0fee12d7d9d50f7bb40808f847","tid":2051011,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"不過今晚集會就見到大部分人都唔係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c8d9072eab1b29d095514b3515b0706f26da77","tid":2051011,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff461769b0d9bdbef4a0934dcb748a5ecfa4e8a","tid":2051011,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"如果今次係最後一次64紀念，咁日日都要係六四。集合所有六四暴行資料，放入區塊鏈永久保存！"},{"pid":"490aa7ad578fcb90550e56fcd187f87ed5fc1d75","tid":2051011,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"64係國際戰線好重要一環"},{"pid":"295ad25b0414b11446c4daeaeb65d88da190d3ae","tid":2051011,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b081ca27c4a356394db04a07a49ae6b819647eb","tid":2051011,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}